data.title: SXSW 2020 Schedule
data.meta_description:
SXSW 2024 Schedule | High Heavens is a new band from veteran Austin musicians, formerly of I Love You But I've Chosen Darkness, Glorium, New Wet Kojak, Edsel, Ignorance Park and Crime in Choir. Bonding over classic psych and kosmische, girl groups, primitive soul and glam, the band
first performed in November 2018 and released its first single in Sept. 2019. High Heavens is John Matthew Walker (vocals), Ernest Salaz (guitar), Jeremy Erwin (keyboards), Jonathan Skaggs (bass), and Nick Pellicciotto (drums).
data.text:

first performed in November 2018 and released its first single in Sept. 2019. High Heavens is John Matthew Walker (vocals), Ernest Salaz (guitar), Jeremy Erwin (keyboards), Jonathan Skaggs (bass), and Nick Pellicciotto (drums).
